lead_paragraph: Chris Carter hit his first home run for Milwaukee, then had a tiebreaking sacrifice fly in the seventh inning to lead the Brewers over the San Francisco Giants 4-3 Wednesday.

headline.print_headline: Carter Homer, Sacrifice Fly Lift Brewers Over Giants 4-3
